Output contract:

Return exactly one JSON object:
{
  "case_id": "<copy input id exactly; this is the neutral prompt-visible id>",
  "schema_decision": "CAUSAL_SCHEMA_REPAIR" | "NO_CAUSAL_SCHEMA_REPAIR" | "UNCLEAR_SCHEMA_EVIDENCE",
